<plot>Craig (a very young Craig Bierko) is a popular High School student bored because he isn't making a difference. Darby (a very young Sally Murphy) suddenly shows up at school, with an apparent chip on her shoulder. Eventually, Craig finds out that Darby has terminal cancer. The romance is short as Darby is bitter about how her life is being taken from her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344842</url></doc>
